                <h1>Exploring Paganism: Nature-Based Spirituality</h1>
                <p>Paganism encompasses a diverse range of spiritual and religious practices characterized by a reverence for nature, polytheism, and ancestral traditions. Often rooted in ancient beliefs, modern paganism celebrates seasonal festivals, rituals, and personal spirituality, fostering a strong connection to the earth and the cosmos.</p>
